[{"Code":"en","Title":"[Industries] Prohibited and High-Risk","Slug":"prohibited-and-high-risk-industries","ContentType":2,"Content":"<blockquote style=\"background:#ddf7ff;border-left:4px solid #006a8a;overflow:auto;\" data-block-id=\"mg92v1a2-7qqn1g-013\" class=\"infoBox\" data-background=\"#ddf7ff\" data-border=\"#006a8a\"><div class=\"blockquote-title\"><p data-block-id=\"mg92v3dn-j0fqhy-026\">Guidelines:</p></div><ul data-block-id=\"mg92v58j-1m7exz-029\"><li data-block-id=\"mg92v58j-yxmn6d-030\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mg92v58j-jet3rg-031\"><strong><u>For high-risk industries</u></strong>, merchants will go through an additional process and be required to provide additional documents as part of due diligence (e.g., a sectoral license) and compliance approval.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mg92v58j-n1gg2j-034\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mg92v58j-skziq0-035\"><strong><u>For prohibited industries</u>,</strong> merchants are <strong>not allowed to onboard.</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mg92v58j-tr6vxq-036\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mg92v58j-orxfae-037\"><strong><u>Xendit Group</u></strong> collectively refers to all our entities and markets.Your title goes here</p></li></ul></blockquote><p><iframe src=\"https://airtable.com/embed/appl7HiZHa3aAJhMr/shrcc9IqFigzzOEWo\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title=\"\" style=\"background:transparent;border:1px solid #ccc;width:100%;height:533px;display:flex;margin-right:auto;\" width=\"100%\" height=\"533\" onmousewheel=\"\" class=\"airtable-embed\"></iframe></p>","SeoTitle":"[Industries] Prohibited and High-Risk","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"[Industri] yang Dilarang dan Berisiko Tinggi","Slug":"prohibited-and-high-risk-industries","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><blockquote style=\"background:#ddf7ff;border-left:4px solid #006a8a;overflow:auto;\" data-block-id=\"mg92v1a2-7qqn1g-013\" class=\"infoBox\" data-background=\"#ddf7ff\" data-border=\"#006a8a\"><div class=\"blockquote-title\"><p data-block-id=\"mg92v3dn-j0fqhy-026\">Panduan:</p></div><ul data-block-id=\"mg92v58j-1m7exz-029\"><li data-block-id=\"mg92v58j-yxmn6d-030\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mg92v58j-jet3rg-031\"><strong><u>Untuk industri berisiko tinggi</u></strong>, merchant akan melalui proses tambahan dan diwajibkan untuk menyediakan dokumen tambahan sebagai bagian dari uji tuntas (due diligence) (misalnya, lisensi sektoral) dan persetujuan kepatuhan (compliance).</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mg92v58j-n1gg2j-034\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mg92v58j-skziq0-035\"><strong><u>Untuk industri yang dilarang</u>,</strong> merchant <strong>tidak diizinkan untuk melakukan onboarding.</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mg92v58j-tr6vxq-036\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mg92v58j-orxfae-037\"><strong><u>Xendit Group</u></strong> secara kolektif mengacu pada semua entitas dan pasar kami.Judul Anda di sini</p></li></ul></blockquote><p><iframe src=\"https://airtable.com/embed/appl7HiZHa3aAJhMr/shrcc9IqFigzzOEWo\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title style=\"background:transparent;border:1px solid #ccc;width:100%;height:533px;display:flex;margin-right:auto;\" width=\"100%\" height=\"533\" onmousewheel class=\"airtable-embed\"></iframe></p>","SeoTitle":"[Industri] yang Dilarang dan Berisiko Tinggi","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"[อุตสาหกรรม] ต้องห้ามและความเสี่ยงสูง","Slug":"prohibited-and-high-risk-industries","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><blockquote style=\"background:#ddf7ff;border-left:4px solid #006a8a;overflow:auto;\" data-block-id=\"mg92v1a2-7qqn1g-013\" class=\"infoBox\" data-background=\"#ddf7ff\" data-border=\"#006a8a\"><div class=\"blockquote-title\"><p data-block-id=\"mg92v3dn-j0fqhy-026\">แนวทางปฏิบัติ:</p></div><ul data-block-id=\"mg92v58j-1m7exz-029\"><li data-block-id=\"mg92v58j-yxmn6d-030\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mg92v58j-jet3rg-031\"><strong><u>สำหรับอุตสาหกรรมที่มีความเสี่ยงสูง</u></strong> ร้านค้าจะต้องผ่านกระบวนการเพิ่มเติมและต้องจัดเตรียมเอกสารเพิ่มเติมซึ่งเป็นส่วนหนึ่งของการตรวจสอบวิเคราะห์สถานะ (due diligence) (เช่น ใบอนุญาตเฉพาะทางอุตสาหกรรม) และการอนุมัติด้านการปฏิบัติตามกฎระเบียบ (compliance approval)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mg92v58j-n1gg2j-034\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mg92v58j-skziq0-035\"><strong><u>สำหรับอุตสาหกรรมที่ถูกห้าม</u>,</strong> ร้านค้า <strong>ไม่ได้รับอนุญาตให้เข้าร่วม (onboard)</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mg92v58j-tr6vxq-036\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mg92v58j-orxfae-037\"><strong><u>Xendit Group</u></strong> หมายถึงหน่วยงานและตลาดทั้งหมดของเราโดยรวมYour title goes here</p></li></ul></blockquote><p><iframe src=\"https://airtable.com/embed/appl7HiZHa3aAJhMr/shrcc9IqFigzzOEWo\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title style=\"background:transparent;border:1px solid #ccc;width:100%;height:533px;display:flex;margin-right:auto;\" width=\"100%\" height=\"533\" onmousewheel class=\"airtable-embed\"></iframe></p>","SeoTitle":"[อุตสาหกรรม] ต้องห้ามและความเสี่ยงสูง","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"[Industrias] Prohibidas y de Alto Riesgo","Slug":"prohibited-and-high-risk-industries","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><blockquote style=\"background:#ddf7ff;border-left:4px solid #006a8a;overflow:auto;\" data-block-id=\"mg92v1a2-7qqn1g-013\" class=\"infoBox\" data-background=\"#ddf7ff\" data-border=\"#006a8a\"><div class=\"blockquote-title\"><p data-block-id=\"mg92v3dn-j0fqhy-026\">Pautas:</p></div><ul data-block-id=\"mg92v58j-1m7exz-029\"><li data-block-id=\"mg92v58j-yxmn6d-030\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mg92v58j-jet3rg-031\"><strong><u>Para industrias de alto riesgo</u></strong>, los comercios pasarán por un proceso adicional y se les requerirá proporcionar documentos adicionales como parte de la diligencia debida (por ejemplo, una licencia sectorial) y la aprobación de cumplimiento.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mg92v58j-n1gg2j-034\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mg92v58j-skziq0-035\"><strong><u>Para industrias prohibidas</u>,</strong> los comercios <strong>no tienen permitido darse de alta.</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"mg92v58j-tr6vxq-036\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"mg92v58j-orxfae-037\"><strong><u>Xendit Group</u></strong> se refiere colectivamente a todas nuestras entidades y mercados.Su título va aquí</p></li></ul></blockquote><p><iframe src=\"https://airtable.com/embed/appl7HiZHa3aAJhMr/shrcc9IqFigzzOEWo\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" title style=\"background:transparent;border:1px solid #ccc;width:100%;height:533px;display:flex;margin-right:auto;\" width=\"100%\" height=\"533\" onmousewheel class=\"airtable-embed\"></iframe></p>","SeoTitle":"[Industrias] Prohibidas y de Alto Riesgo","Description":null}]